headline: Can Netflix Stock Continue to Soar in 2025?
summary: Netflix is one of the few technology stocks that didn't experience a sell-off during the initial tariff announcements in April.  Its stock trades at a premium to other companies in streaming and entertainment, but management's long-term vision might justify that.  2025 has more or less been a wash for technology stocks.
